<p><a id="TSJN-01-05-0765-kw-0001" class="keywordref" title="jump to I lately wrote to your excellency in text" href="#TSJN-01-05-0765-ks-0001">I lately wrote to your excellency</a>: This was, no doubt, a letter written by Lee in response to <a href="default.xqy?keys=TSJN-print-01-05-02-0581" class="document">TJs of 16 Apr. 1781</a>, q.v.; it has not been found.</p></div>
